  {rating: 5, comment: "How do you fight a nemesis that you can't see? If you shoot first, you're the devil. If you don't, then you're dead. The Hurt Locker shows that everyone has their limits when the possibility of death reveals itself every damn day.\r\n\r\nThe hurt locker is a modern war thriller, set in Baghdad in 2004. The film revolves around a soldier hired to do a job even more dangerous than shooting and dodging bullets: defusing bombs! William James is the replacement leader for the bomb disposal unit. A wild man who defused over 800 bombs & still counting and he seems not only indifferent to the dangers of his job, he absolutely revels in the dangers. He is the man who loves the battlefield more than his family. ", user_id: 1, movie_id: 7, recommend: 1},
