  {rating: 4, comment: "Favorite Robert De Niro movie!!!\r\n\r\nJust kidding, however very funny and always a great film to watch with the whole family. De Niro and Stiller are as hilarious as they were in the first film, and Dustin Hoffman and Barbra Streisand are a delightfully funny new addition to the franchise.", user_id: 1, movie_id: 22, recommend: 1},
