  {rating: 5, comment: "This movie started off with Charlie Babbitt (Tom Cruise) being a big greedy jerk that worked for an exotic car dealership. When he learns his father dies and the inheritance of 3 million dollars is given to a man named Raymond, he goes back home only to discover he has an older brother who is an autistic savant (an autistic person but with genius abilities) and wants his money, but they both go on an amazing adventure that changes both of their lives. This movie is very beautiful and touching. I definitely loved watching this movie!", user_id: 1, movie_id: 30, recommend: 1},
