  {rating: 5, comment: "10 out of 10 this movie is amazing not only does this movie have a good message but the songs and costumes are amazing props to them now the acting by Jane Russell and Marilyn Monroe is pretty good they both sell there characters in an amazing way and The pink gown Marilyn wears still has a big impact on today I would recommend this movie to anyone 10/10", user_id: 1, movie_id: 31, recommend: 1},
  {rating: 5, comment: "You'll have a lot of fun while watching that and you're gonna find the serious thing at the end it's sooo great", user_id: 1, movie_id: 31, recommend: 1},
  {rating: 5, comment: "Charlie And The Chocolate Factory is a mouth-watering, epic comeback from the vastly disappointing original. The movie is truly a fantastical rollercoaster of chocolatey goodness. It absolutely blows the 1971 Gene Wilder movie out of the water with its perfect set design, faithfulness to its source and its hit of that Tim Burton twisted magic that we all know and love! For those many of us that were disappointed by the old movie, you're in for a treat with this one! Its got the wondrous trio of Tim burton, Roald Dahl and Johnny Depp and it actually has a nut room making it way more like the book and way more like we'd imagined it! Enjoy this movie, it really is the only true adaption of this beautiful book!", user_id: 1, movie_id: 32, recommend: 1},
  {rating: 5, comment: "This movie just doesn’t age. I don’t know how many times I’ve watched this film and I find new things to enjoy. Upon its release, its rather brazen approach by critics everywhere felt like they got together before their reviews to bash the living stuff out of it and burn it to the ground. Little by little, more people than critics then began criticizing it and felt it simply wasn’t Willy Wonka-esque, whatever that means. Those looking for the same nostalgia as the original will be disappointed for sure—-the eras are extremely different and to be honest, the original was so much worse. Tim Burton and Johnny Depp has created a zany experience that has stood the test of time as much as the original has. ", user_id: 1, movie_id: 32, recommend: 1}
